<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 06:09:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登突然访问后，以色列北部边境和西岸局势在一夜之间升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-live/escalation-on-israels-northern-border-continues-overnight-after-snap-biden-visit/0000018b-456d-d614-abcf-ed7fca660000</link><description>美国总统拜登在战时访问以色列后就哈马斯袭击问题在椭圆形办公室发表讲话 ■ 英国首相苏纳克将在特拉维夫会见内塔尼亚胡 ■ 500 名美国犹太人在国会大厦举行的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动中被捕 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯： 3,200 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 05:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-live/escalation-on-israels-northern-border-continues-overnight-after-snap-biden-visit/0000018b-456d-d614-abcf-ed7fca660000</guid></item><item><title>以色列两名男子在不同事件中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/20-year-old-man-shot-dead-in-arab-town-in-israels-south/0000018b-4623-df22-a5eb-4f7bc0560000</link><description>警方正在调查拉哈特和阿卡事件的情况，第二名男子的身份仍然未知。自今年年初以来，以色列阿拉伯社区已发生200多起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 04:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/20-year-old-man-shot-dead-in-arab-town-in-israels-south/0000018b-4623-df22-a5eb-4f7bc0560000</guid></item><item><title>我会见了世界上最重要的犹太复国主义领导人：拜登总统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/i-met-the-most-important-zionist-leader-in-the-world-president-biden/0000018b-4464-df22-a5eb-4d7da45b0000</link><description>这位美国总统证明，他是以色列领导层的对立面——首先是内塔尼亚胡——他们没有同情心，对公民的痛苦没有同情心，也无法提供真诚的安慰之词</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/i-met-the-most-important-zionist-leader-in-the-world-president-biden/0000018b-4464-df22-a5eb-4d7da45b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡必须遵守拜登的规则，以确保美国的支持和威慑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-to-play-by-bidens-rules-to-ensure-american-support-and-deterrence/0000018b-4465-de3d-a58f-cc6ddc6b0000</link><description>通过坚持为加沙建立人道主义走廊，拜登向以色列规定了新的游戏规则，以色列需要美国的威慑，这样伊朗和黎巴嫩就不会受到诱惑加入战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-to-play-by-bidens-rules-to-ensure-american-support-and-deterrence/0000018b-4465-de3d-a58f-cc6ddc6b0000</guid></item><item><title>在贝埃里基布兹，时间静止了。大屠杀前的生命证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/on-kibbutz-beeri-time-stood-still-evidence-of-life-before-the-massacre/0000018b-4465-d242-abef-566704e70000</link><description>喝了一半的咖啡、一张关于医生预约的便条和冰箱里仍然装满了食物，这些都为 10 月 7 日恐怖事件发生之前这个繁荣的基布兹的生活提供了令人毛骨悚然的证据</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 23:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/on-kibbutz-beeri-time-stood-still-evidence-of-life-before-the-massacre/0000018b-4465-d242-abef-566704e70000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-44db-d242-abef-56fff1090000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 22:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-44db-d242-abef-56fff1090000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争必须立即停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-must-stop-immediately/0000018b-43ec-d614-abcf-ebff3ecd0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 21:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-must-stop-immediately/0000018b-43ec-d614-abcf-ebff3ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>西方左派不是虚伪，而是疯狂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-western-left-isnt-hypocritical-its-deranged/0000018b-4411-d242-abef-56379cbb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 21:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-western-left-isnt-hypocritical-its-deranged/0000018b-4411-d242-abef-56379cbb0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登展示了美国对以色列及其安全的承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/biden-demonstrated-americas-commitment-to-israel-and-its-security/0000018b-4449-df22-a5eb-4d79e7ce0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:57:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/biden-demonstrated-americas-commitment-to-israel-and-its-security/0000018b-4449-df22-a5eb-4d79e7ce0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登授予以色列的巨大胡萝卜旁边悬着一根大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/a-big-stick-hovers-beside-the-huge-carrots-being-granted-to-israel-by-biden/0000018b-4466-de3d-a58f-cc6f6b370000</link><description>以色列执政党的部长和立法者敦促他管好自己的事，不要干涉我们的生活并尊重我们的民主，拜登以一种不亚于历史性的方式团结在我们一边</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/a-big-stick-hovers-beside-the-huge-carrots-being-granted-to-israel-by-biden/0000018b-4466-de3d-a58f-cc6f6b370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为加沙边境社区撤离人员提供创伤支持的计划依赖于志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-trauma-support-to-evacuees-of-gaza-border-communities-relies-on-volunteers/0000018b-4442-d614-abcf-ec73a55a0000</link><description>精神病医院的管理人员紧急呼吁志愿者，因为他们有限的人员无法为撤离者提供情绪急救。专家和组织在过去十年中多次警告说，公共心理健康系统正在被摧毁</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-trauma-support-to-evacuees-of-gaza-border-communities-relies-on-volunteers/0000018b-4442-d614-abcf-ec73a55a0000</guid></item><item><title>共和党在参议院听证会上猛烈抨击拜登下一任美国驻以色列大使候选人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/gop-hammers-bidens-candidate-for-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel-in-senate-hearing/0000018b-43e1-de3d-a58f-cbe9aad40000</link><description>共和党的攻击发生在拜登政府提名卢的关键考虑因素之一之际，即在国会在推动提名人前进方面遇到前所未有的困难的情况下，他通过确认程序的潜在能力</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 18:25:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/gop-hammers-bidens-candidate-for-next-u-s-ambassador-to-israel-in-senate-hearing/0000018b-43e1-de3d-a58f-cbe9aad40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人需要的不仅仅是“摧毁哈马斯”的模糊要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israelis-need-more-than-a-vague-demand-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-43dc-df22-a5eb-4bfdecc10000</link><description>在第二次世界大战最黑暗的时期，罗斯福和丘吉尔规划了战后的未来。现在是政府提出以色列愿景的时候了，为了这个愿景，数百万士兵和平民被要求冒着生命危险，甚至牺牲生命</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 18:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-opinion/israelis-need-more-than-a-vague-demand-to-destroy-hamas/0000018b-43dc-df22-a5eb-4bfdecc10000</guid></item><item><title>对于哈马斯来说，加沙医院悲剧是一次叙事胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</link><description>越来越多的证据更加有力地证明了以色列关于加沙城阿赫利圣公会医院悲剧如何发生的说法，但损害已经造成。与此同时，加沙人将埋葬他们的死者，他们已成为国际影响力游戏中的棋子</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</guid></item><item><title>新发现改变了哈薛国王攻击圣经迦特的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</link><description>迦特的非利士人被认为是黎凡特地区使用美索不达米亚风格的烧砖建筑的异类。但在 Tell es-Safi 烧制砖块的并不是窑炉</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在对以色列进行史无前例的战时访问期间回顾了大屠杀和9月11日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</link><description>美国总统宣称“10 月 7 日是自大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天”，并发誓“不会再袖手旁观，什么也不做，今天不会，明天不会，永远不会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</guid></item><item><title>数万人签署请愿书，要求驱逐被视为亲哈马斯的美国教授</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</link><description>康奈尔大学、哥伦比亚大学和耶鲁大学的教职人员要求解雇那些将哈马斯对以色列南部的袭击形容为令人振奋和震惊的研究员。耶鲁大学的一位教授说：“巴勒斯坦人完全有权通过武装斗争进行抵抗”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</guid></item><item><title>“如果她落入哈马斯手中，我们不知道她将如何在克罗恩病中生存”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特殊项目 ■ Tamar Gutman 很高兴。在与一种使人衰弱的疾病抗争了几年后，她精神焕发，很高兴能够参加超新星音乐节。她的家人谈论她以及收集信息的尝试</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府未批准解决巴勒斯坦囚犯过度拥挤问题的临时计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</link><description>十六名以色列立法者投票赞成这项临时规定，该规定将持续三个月，并使该国的监狱即使在满负荷的情况下也能接纳新囚犯</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:42:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</guid></item><item><title>17名记者确认在以色列、加沙和黎巴嫩死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/17-journalists-confirmed-dead-in-israel-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-4311-d614-abcf-eb7349530000</link><description>保护记者委员会周三表示，自 10 月 7 日哈马斯在以色列南部发动致命袭击以来，已有 3 名以色列记者、1 名黎巴嫩记者和 13 名巴勒斯坦记者死亡。有关其他记者被杀、失踪、拘留、受伤或威胁的报道正在接受调查</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/17-journalists-confirmed-dead-in-israel-gaza-and-lebanon/0000018b-4311-d614-abcf-eb7349530000</guid></item></channel></rss>